<p>So… long story short, I ended up in hospital. Boo!</p>
<p>Nothing too serious, (I tell you all about it the video)… but while I was there I thought it’d be fun to film a brand new lesson for you focusing on how and why transcribing is SO important… showing you my own personal transcribing process… plus, exactly how long it takes me.</p>
